---
title: Chicken Caesar Burger & Kumara Fries for Dinner with a Creamy Chicken Caesar Salad for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual, then put a new spin on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! We've got chicken Caesar doing double duty tonight, as a tasty burger for dinner and then a hearty salad for lunch. Extra delicious!

